    <td class="rowodd" valign="top" width="2000">A lot of changes and improvments have been made since the last release 6 years ago: folding friendly, doesn't mess with history and registers, utf-8 friendly, new mapping to replace a placeholder with its contents, options to select (or not) the current marker on a jump ; Surround() recognizes placeholders from other selections, support for angle brackets ; new context sensitive text inserters ; etc.</td>
</tr>
