    <td class="roweven" valign="top" width="2000">(*) Misc_maps: Some minor problems fixed. <br>(*) Markers: Names of options and functions changed ; Closing markers can be of any length ; Possibility to jump backward and forward from markers to markers + the associated commands.<br>(*) Mappings can be customized outside the plugins.<br>(*) Doc updated</td>
</tr>
